Installation instructions
=========================

Django-Jython installation follows the typical distutils-based procedure. Go
into the root directory of the unpacked the source distribution and run::

  $ jython setup.py install

That's all.


http://bugs.jython.org/issue1110

A simple two line change is necessary to resolve the issue; a patch is attached to the above bug.
Easy Install?

Alternatively, if you already have setuptools working on your Jython installation, you can use it too:

$ jython /path/to/easy_install django-jython 
